parameters: Oh... What's wrong, Vita? Did you forget something?

Um... the stuffed animal... I bought it together with you when
you were born...
スライドスピード = def

If time is limited... then while you can, make the important
people in your life happy...
Good morning, Vita. Your mother has already left.

\SE[3]I see... Today, Mom had work. \SE[1]Dad, what do you want
to eat today? Should I go catch a wild boar like usual?
No, today... Hmm. Something light would be good...

\SE[2]Ah... I see...? \SE[39]I guess something light... What
should I do? Maybe mushrooms would be fine...?

Ah... If you're the one preparing it, then anything would make me
happy.

\SE[4]Then... how about a cave...? I think we might be able to
find something there.
スライドスピード = def

Hey, before you leave, how about giving your father a I'm off
kiss?

\SE[4]Huh? What's this all of a sudden? Don't we not have such a
custom at home...?

It seems like it's normal in Cordain. The soldiers were talking
about it.
\SE[9]Hmm... a kiss, huh... I'm a little hesitant...

How about a hug then? It seems like they have that kind of thing
in their theater over there.

\SE[2]Hmm... If it's just that...? \SE[46]Well, I guess there's
no helping it...
スライドスピード = def
Ah... I'm satisfied... Take care on your journey.
\SE[0]Hmm... I'll go get some food, so look forward to it.
Ah... I'm looking forward to it.
スライドスピード = def

A kind wife... and a daughter... It was a happiness that was too
good for me...

\SE[1]Good morning! What should we do today? Shall I take you
somewhere?
おとうさんとおるすばん
I decided to bring a stuffed animal with me!

\SE[12]We're in this together. Even if it means going to hell,
I'll have you by my side.
おとうさんとおるすばん

\SE[14]I'm entrusting you with the task of watching over your
father. If anything happens, protect him in my place.
